# [L1:bad] Bad Domain

## Purpose

A domain with broken code references.

## Entry Points

| Entry Point | Description |
|-------------|-------------|
| [`missing_func`](../../sample_code/src/example.py#L99) | Function that does not exist |
| [`wrong_line`](../../sample_code/src/example.py#L200) | Symbol at wrong line |
| [`no_such_symbol`](../../sample_code/src/example.py#L5) | Symbol name doesn't exist |
